<p style="margin-top: 12px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><strong>Hello {!Case.Casecontact},</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Thank you for your business! We are writing to confirm that we&rsquo;ve received your order, <span class="highlight" style="color: #c53223;"><strong>{!Case.Case_Ref_ID__c}</strong></span>, <em>for the following items:</em></span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 4px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><strong>Order Summary:</strong></span></p>
<hr style="margin-top: 0px;" />
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Order placed: May 20, 2015</span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"> PO#: if applicable</span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"> Order #: <span class="highlight" style="color: #c53223;"><strong>{!Case.Case_Ref_ID__c}</strong></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 4px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><strong>Order Status:</strong></span></p>
<hr style="margin-top: 0px;" />
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">You can track the status of this order, and all of your orders, online by visiting <span class="highlight" style="color: #c53223;"><a style="color: #c53223; text-decoration: none;" href="http://tonyblake.com/TESTsites/honeywell_email/SFDC/SFDC_tempate_01_Debug2.html#">Honeywell&rsquo;s Order Status</a></span>.</span></p>
<p style="margin-right: 50px; margin-left: 50px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><span class="chevron" style="color: #c53223;"><strong>&gt;&gt;</strong></span><strong> Did you forget to attach your PO to the original request?</strong> </span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"> No problem. <span class="highlight">Just reply to this email and attach your PO.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-right: 50px; margin-left: 50px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><span class="chevron" style="color: #c53223;"><strong>&gt;&gt;</strong></span><strong> Next time, put us to work faster by using the portal - 12 hours vs. a few seconds. </strong>That&rsquo;s the difference in confirmation times between ordering by email or using Honeywell&rsquo;s newly improved My Aerospace web portal! In the future, please visit www.MyAerospace.com to place an order, and within seconds receive your conformation number, tracking data, and scheduled delivery information.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 4px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><strong>Questions</strong></span></p>
<hr style="margin-top: 0px;" />
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">We&rsquo;ve connected all of your order details through the subject line of this email. That subject line was created specifically for you and is unique to this order.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">So, please leave the subject line unchanged should you reply to make sure your response is routed immediately to this case.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 4px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Thanks again! We appreciate your business, </span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><strong>Honeywell Aerospace</strong></span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 4px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">{!Case.Case_Ref_ID__c}</span></p>
